<HEADLINE> URGENT 4: Flag Lowering and Raising Begins at Handover Ceremony </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The flag lowering and raising ceremony signifying Hong Kong's
handover begins.
</P>
<P>
Flag guards from the Chinese and British sides have earlier
entered the venue of the ceremony. Under the flagpoles on the
rostrum, Chinese flag guards disply to all people present China's
national flag and the regional flag of the Hong Kong Special
Administrative Region featuring a bauhinia that will soon be
raised.
</P>
</TEXT>
