<HEADLINE> URGENT 11: Hong Kong Enters New Era of development: Jiang </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
"July 1, 1997 will go down in the annals of history as a day
that merits eternal memory. The return of Hong Kong to the
motherland after going through more than a century of vicissitudes
indicates that from now on, Hong Kong compatriots have become true
masters of this Chinese land and that Hong Kong has now entered a
new era of development," said Chinese president Jiang Zemin at the
Hong Kong handover ceremony.
</P>
