<BODY>
<HEADLINE> URGENT 13: Hong Kong to Develop Democracy Suiting Its Reality </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Hong Kong SAR shall gradually develop a democratic system
that suits Hong Kong's reality, said Chinese president Jiang Zemin
today.
</P>
<P>
He noted that after Hong Kong's return, the Chinese Government
shall be responsible for foreign affairs relating to Hong Kong and
the defense of Hong Kong, while the Hong Kong SAR shall be vested,
in accordance with the Basic Law, with executive power,
legislative power and independent judicial power, including that
of final adjudication, and Hong Kong people shall enjoy various
rights and freedoms in accordance with law.
</P>
</TEXT>
