<HEADLINE> Peres Hails Hong Kong's Return to China </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
JERUSALEM, July 1 (Xinhua) -- Former Israeli prime minister
Shimon Peres has expressed his warm congratulations to China on
the return of Hong Kong to the motherland.
</P>
<P>
Speaking at the opening ceremony of a photo exhibition in
Ramat Gan Monday night, Peres, who is also president of the
council for the promotion of Israel-China Relations, said that
