<HEADLINE> Myanmar Leader Congratulates China on Hong Kong's Return </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, July 1 (Xinhua) -- Chairman of Myanmar's State Law and
Order Restoration Council (head of state), Than Shwe, sent a
message, on Monday, of congratulations to Chinese President Jiang
Zemin on Hong Kong's return to the motherland.
