<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Philippine President Hails HK's Return to China </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, July 1 (Xinhua) -- Philippine President Fidel Ramos
sent a message of congratulations today to Chinese President Jiang
Zemin on Hong Kong's return to the motherland.
</P>
<P>
Ramos said he believed that under the principles of "one
country, two systems", "Hong Kong people governing Hong Kong" and
"a high degree of autonomy," China's resumption of the exercise of
sovereignty over Hong Kong would make contributions to the
stability and progress of Hong Kong, China's inland areas and the
Asia-Pacific region.
</P>
<P>
He expressed confidence in the stability of the Hong Kong
Special Administrative Region as well as Hong Kong's future.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
