The Times:
</P>
<P>
-- Britain yielded Hong Kong to China on Monday night in
ceremonies which were by turns extraordinarily emotional and
austere.
</P>
<P>
The Financial Times:
</P>
<P>
-- A brief handshake between Prince Charles and President Jiang
