empire as Hong Kong was returned to China.
</P>
<P>
The Daily Telegraph:
</P>
<P>
-- At the stroke of midnight, 156 years of British colonial
rule over Hong Kong came to an end.
</P>
<P>
The Independent:
</P>
<P>
-- Never has there been such an extraordinary end to British
rule, full of so many mixed emotions. 
</P>
