easily throw them out as constituencies wanted serious
representation in parliament.
</P>
<P>
Addressing the legislators on the eve of the opening of the
third session of the fourth parliament of Zimbabwe here last
night, Mugabe told the MPs that their seats were not guaranteed
as the people had the final choice.
</P>
