several terms depending on your viability. But people are your
judges and they can be fed up with you and throw you out of
parliament."
</P>
<P>
Mugabe said there was a need to concentrate more on rural
development, saying Zimbabwe could not talk of development when
the rural areas remained underdeveloped.
</P>
<P>
He said he wanted to see government funding for various
projects in each province starting this year. He said Minister of
Finance Herbert Murerwa had been committed to the plan. 
