<HEADLINE> hkhk - PLA Air Force Helicopters Land at Shek Kong Air Base </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, July 1 (Xinhua) -- Six Chinese military helicopters
landed safely at Shek Kong Air Base in the "New Territories" at
08:37 this morning.
</P>
<P>
This is the first time the military aircraft of New China
touched down on Hong Kong's soil.
</P>
<P>
Shek Kong Air Base is located in the northern part of the "New
Territories", which witnessed a number of heroic battles to resist
the British colonial rule.  
