<BODY>
<HEADLINE> hkhk - URGENT: PLA Garrison Ground Forces Enter Hong Kong </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, July 1 (Xinhua) -- Ground forces of the Hong Kong
Garrison of the Chinese People's Liberation Army (PLA) entered
Hong Kong at 6 a.m. today via three checkpoints at Man Kam To,
Huanggang and Sha Tau Kok.
</P>
<P>
At the same time, the air and naval forces of the PLA Garrison
also were heading for Hong Kong's sea and air space. 
</P>
</TEXT>
